listitem.para:
Video decoding via FFMPEG;
            xjadeo supports a multitude of 
            file-formats and video codecs.

entry.para:
specify how to 'convert' MTC SMPTE to framenumber:
                0: use framerate of MTC clock (default);
                2: use video file FPS;
                3: "resample": videoFPS / MTC
                (-M,midi sync)

section.para:
using the set override remote-control command,
        it is possible to disable certain key-bindings or window-events.
        and limit user interation with the window.

